long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you automatically block words that may cause your search on the Tehran Tower website to yield incorrect results.
When you need to search for construction projects in Tehran Tower, entering the project name may sometimes lead to mistakes that prevent you from finding the desired page. In this extension, we have blocked certain keywords to make your search easier and avoid any issues that might arise during your search.
